<p>This is a fucking wild moment for me. Don't even know what to say, so I may as well cut to the chase.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Thanks&nbsp;to&nbsp;(deep&nbsp;breath)...</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;holy&nbsp;shit&nbsp;that's&nbsp;a&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;people</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;">Shaggydredlocks</a></span>: Without all of your crit on SCP-2417 the Church of the Second Hytoth would be absolutely nothing like how it is today. I can't give nowhere near enough credit for it.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;">LordStonefish</a></span>: For writing for the group early in its development and helping me realize that this is something more people would want to write about.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;">Modern_Erasmus</a></span>: The advice you gave me about focusing more on the alien side of the Church to make the group feel more unique was some of the best advice I've received and has massively influenced how I've written the group since.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1698079&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Metaphysician" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1698079)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;">Metaphysician</a></span>: Your knack at worldbuilding has and always will be an inspiration for all of the Ortothan worldbuilding I write.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3027978); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3027978); return false;">mlister</a></span>: For always keeping me encouraged to keep pushing on with the group and for their feedback.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rat-lord" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2433554); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2433554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Rat Lord" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2433554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rat-lord" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2433554); return false;">Rat Lord</a></span>: HATEFUL STAR 2: APOCALYPSE BOOGALOO</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span>: For all of their edits to the layout of this hub, its CSS, and their advice on how to best present the information here. Without them this hub be nothing like how it is today.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;">OthellotheCat</a></span>: For being the #1 Terzan 2 fanboy.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/panteradactyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000286); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000286&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Panteradactyl" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000286)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/panteradactyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000286); return false;">Panteradactyl</a></span>: For coming up with ideas regarding alien cultures and concepts.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmacro" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3296783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3296783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="DrMacro" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3296783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmacro" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3296783); return false;">DrMacro</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcendres" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2288113); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2288113&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="DrCendres" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2288113)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcendres" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2288113); return false;">DrCendres</a></span>: I can't express just how giddy I was when I saw your team's CotSH contest articles. Seriously. It made my day.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taoka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4076464); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4076464&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Taoka" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4076464)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taoka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4076464); return false;">Taoka</a></span>: For designing the Church logo based on my crummy sketches of it (I love your work on it so heckin' much).</li>
<li>All of this hub's critters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;">Elogee FishTruck</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;">DrChandra</a></span>, and the rest who gave it lookovers &#8212; can't remember everyone just yet.</li>
<li>And to everyone else who has expressed interest in the group along the way.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
