<p>The Second Hytoth logo was created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taoka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4076464); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4076464&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1551464033" alt="Taoka" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4076464)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taoka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4076464); return false;">Taoka</a></span> and the SoI-002 illustration was drawn by myself, both released under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 License.</p>
