<p>I was thinking about having some long post here to commemorate this, probably about how after 2 years of work this is finally done, but nothing comes to mind. This is a deeply personal moment for me and it's thanks to the wiki that this can happen.</p>
<p>Anyways I'm now gonna go pass out.</p>

